    "description": "If you're reading this, then you probably just died and got thrown out of Heaven. Sorry about that. Good news, though; you get to be on a gameshow!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/7f3336e2e1da1c7ec2cd8679ddb562a3.poster.avif?t=1635585369\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/7f3336e2e1da1c7ec2cd8679ddb562a3.webm?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/7f3336e2e1da1c7ec2cd8679ddb562a3.mp4?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Conquer Hell With Love and Snuggles!</strong><br>Fall For You is a rhythm-based roguelike. Move and attack with the beat to power up, win the hearts of every damned soul you meet, traverse perilous obstacle courses, win fabulous prizes that change the way you play, and cuddle with a scary demon mom to keep yourself going!<br><br><strong>Dance Party!</strong><br>Move it when the kick drum kicks, and attack when the snare drum snares to become faster and more powerful!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/ce32076acd16c8aab5c0549ae3e2ba50.poster.avif?t=1635585369\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/ce32076acd16c8aab5c0549ae3e2ba50.webm?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/ce32076acd16c8aab5c0549ae3e2ba50.mp4?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Friends in Unexpected Places!</strong><br>Shoot fellow damned souls with Cuddle Bullets to earn their admiration! Earn Khaos Roses from your adoring fans that cheer you on below.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/655a8b8ad419ef753c0f29814e430205.poster.avif?t=1635585369\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/655a8b8ad419ef753c0f29814e430205.webm?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/655a8b8ad419ef753c0f29814e430205.mp4?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The World Changes Around You!</strong><br>Stay above the UnderFog, as the world's grid rises and falls around you! Take on procedurally generated platforming challenges to stay in the game and win prizes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/5bbe5912f6265ede588b9402fa3cb278.poster.avif?t=1635585369\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/5bbe5912f6265ede588b9402fa3cb278.webm?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/5bbe5912f6265ede588b9402fa3cb278.mp4?t=1635585369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fabulous Prizes!</strong><br>Save up your Khaos Rozes, and win prizes that change the way you play!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803100/extras/691ad41aa226badc92565c03bbeda7e0.poster.avif?t=1635585369\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as